1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:04,129
<i>Mrs. Roja! How do you respond to</i>
<i>Captain Jacinto's accusations?</i>

2
00:00:04,212 --> 00:00:07,632
<i>A video has surfaced</i>
<i>clearly showing your involvement!</i>

3
00:00:07,716 --> 00:00:09,759
<i>Everyone's question is, why did you do it?</i>

4
00:00:09,843 --> 00:00:12,429
- [GRETA SCREAMING]
- [OFFICER] <i>Emil Padua is in the elevator.</i>

5
00:00:12,512 --> 00:00:15,223
[EMIL GROANING]

6
00:00:15,306 --> 00:00:16,850
[OFFICER] <i>Calling all units.</i>

7
00:00:16,933 --> 00:00:19,352
<i>Emil Padua and his men are on the stairs</i>
<i>leading to the basement.</i>

8
00:00:19,436 --> 00:00:21,855
<i>- I think this is it.</i>
<i>- We need to break through it.</i>

9
00:00:21,938 --> 00:00:23,690
<i>We're running out of time.</i>
<i>Let's just blow this up!</i>

10
00:00:23,773 --> 00:00:25,567
You can't blow it up.

11
00:00:25,650 --> 00:00:27,777
<i>The tunnel will collapse.</i>
<i>We can't do that.</i>

12
00:00:27,861 --> 00:00:29,320
[MAN] <i>I'm grabbing the dynamite.</i>

13
00:00:29,404 --> 00:00:31,448
<i>Dude, don't do it!</i>

14
00:00:31,531 --> 00:00:33,074
[LIAM] <i>I already know the truth.</i>

15
00:00:33,158 --> 00:00:34,826
<i>But I need to hear it from you.</i>

16
00:00:34,909 --> 00:00:36,411
<i>Why did you do it?</i>

17
00:00:36,494 --> 00:00:37,871
[SOBS] <i>I'm sorry.</i>

18
00:00:37,954 --> 00:00:41,291
<i>I was desperate. We're drowning in debt.</i>

19
00:00:42,333 --> 00:00:45,879
<i>Our family's flat-out broke.</i>
<i>I didn't know what to do.</i>

20
00:00:45,962 --> 00:00:47,964
<i>Do you know how many died because of you?!</i>

21
00:00:48,047 --> 00:00:49,549
<i>Where's Magnus?</i>

22
00:00:49,632 --> 00:00:51,426
<i>The police took him.</i>

23
00:00:51,509 --> 00:00:53,261
<i>They think he's Ma'am Greta's accomplice.</i>

24
00:00:54,137 --> 00:00:57,724
<i>Do you think she really had anything</i>
<i>to do with what happened?</i>

25
00:00:57,807 --> 00:00:59,726
<i>There's proof, son.</i>

26
00:00:59,809 --> 00:01:02,479
<i>You need to pay for all of your crimes.</i>

27
00:01:02,562 --> 00:01:05,398
[GRETA] <i>Please! I'm begging you!</i>

28
00:01:05,482 --> 00:01:07,650
<i>Don't you love me anymore?</i>

29
00:01:08,860 --> 00:01:12,655
<i>I'm turning you in to the police</i>
<i>because it's the right thing to do.</i>

30
00:01:12,739 --> 00:01:14,574
<i>That's how you raised me.</i>

31
00:01:14,657 --> 00:01:16,534
<i>It's not that I don't love you.</i>

32
00:01:22,415 --> 00:01:24,209
[CRICKETS CHIRPING IN THE DISTANCE]

33
00:01:24,292 --> 00:01:25,877
[GLOOMY MUSIC PLAYING]

34
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:28,421
[MIKE] Dude, it's too risky!

35
00:01:28,505 --> 00:01:30,256
It's going to collapse! We'll go down--

36
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,008
Dude, come on now!

37
00:01:32,550 --> 00:01:34,344
Hey, that's dangerous!

38
00:01:35,512 --> 00:01:37,263
Dude! Seriously, don't do it!

39
00:01:37,847 --> 00:01:39,140
We can't risk it!

40
00:01:39,224 --> 00:01:40,517
Dude!

41
00:01:41,226 --> 00:01:44,687
- [MINNIE] What's going on?
- Dude, no! Don't use…

42
00:01:44,771 --> 00:01:47,774
Dude, you can't detonate it.

43
00:01:47,857 --> 00:01:49,275
The ground will tremble.

44
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:51,111
The soil won't withstand the impact.

45
00:01:51,194 --> 00:01:52,153
He's right.

46
00:01:52,237 --> 00:01:56,658
We need to establish strong structural
and skeletal support first

47
00:01:56,741 --> 00:01:58,243
to reinforce the ground.

48
00:01:58,326 --> 00:01:59,452
[GOON] What?

49
00:01:59,953 --> 00:02:01,329
Just listen to us.

50
00:02:02,497 --> 00:02:04,332
- Talk to your friend! Please!
- Yes.

51
00:02:04,415 --> 00:02:06,751
- Somebody, please.
- It's a dangerous plan!

52
00:02:06,835 --> 00:02:08,628
We'll go down with it!

53
00:02:08,711 --> 00:02:09,754
[DADO] Come on!

54
00:02:09,838 --> 00:02:12,173
- [GLOOMY MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [EMIL GROANING WEAKLY]

55
00:02:12,757 --> 00:02:14,884
- Papa! Papa!
- [EMIL] Sweetheart!

56
00:02:14,968 --> 00:02:16,010
- Papa.
- [EXHALES HEAVILY]

57
00:02:16,928 --> 00:02:18,221
Don't worry about me.

58
00:02:18,304 --> 00:02:21,516
All that matters now is
that we escape, all right?

59
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:24,269
[GOON] Boss, we tried to break
through the cement.

60
00:02:24,352 --> 00:02:25,812
But it's too hard.

61
00:02:25,895 --> 00:02:27,897
It'll take forever.

62
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:30,650
Let's just blast it so we can get out!

63
00:02:30,733 --> 00:02:32,026
I've already told you many times.

64
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:35,738
What you're planning is dangerous!
That tunnel you built will collapse!

65
00:02:35,822 --> 00:02:37,073
We're all going to get burned!

66
00:02:37,157 --> 00:02:39,617
[DADO] Hey, make up your mind now.

67
00:02:39,701 --> 00:02:41,202
The cops are here.

68
00:02:41,286 --> 00:02:43,580
Will the tunnel really collapse,
or are you just buying time?

69
00:02:43,663 --> 00:02:46,124
- It'll collapse! It's risky!
- [PHONE RINGING]

70
00:02:46,207 --> 00:02:47,542
Hello, Mila?

71
00:02:47,625 --> 00:02:48,793
Lucas.

72
00:02:49,544 --> 00:02:51,421
I'm begging you.

73
00:02:51,504 --> 00:02:53,381
You have to surrender now.

74
00:02:53,464 --> 00:02:54,799
Where are you?

75
00:02:54,883 --> 00:02:56,467
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

76
00:02:56,551 --> 00:02:59,846
We're down in the basement's
mechanical room.

77
00:02:59,929 --> 00:03:01,598
The tunnel's almost done.

78
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,349
- Let's meet at--
- [MAN]<i> Hello.</i>

79
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:07,020
This is General Cabral.

80
00:03:07,103 --> 00:03:09,606
Your wife is in our custody.

81
00:03:10,732 --> 00:03:12,650
You have nowhere to run. Surrender now.

82
00:03:13,401 --> 00:03:15,445
The police know our location.

83
00:03:16,279 --> 00:03:17,530
- Detonate it!
- Roman!

84
00:03:17,614 --> 00:03:19,741
- Roman!
- [MIKE] Please, don't do it!

85
00:03:19,824 --> 00:03:21,826
- [EMIL] Keep watch outside!
- Yes, boss!

86
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:24,662
- [LUCAS GROWLING]
- [BLOWS LANDING]

87
00:03:24,746 --> 00:03:26,998
- [MINNIE] Please stop!
- [MIKE GROANS]

88
00:03:27,081 --> 00:03:28,458
[LUCAS EXCLAIMS]

89
00:03:28,541 --> 00:03:30,376
- [MINNIE] Let him go!
- [SHOUTS ANGRILY]

90
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:31,628
[MINNIE PANTING]

91
00:03:31,711 --> 00:03:32,962
[LUCAS GROWLS]

92
00:03:33,046 --> 00:03:36,257
[FOREBODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

93
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:43,348
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

94
00:03:54,901 --> 00:04:01,866
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

95
00:04:34,315 --> 00:04:39,570
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

96
00:04:39,654 --> 00:04:42,490
[GOON BREATHING HEAVILY]

97
00:04:55,962 --> 00:05:02,176
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

98
00:05:04,095 --> 00:05:05,138
[DOORS OPENING]

99
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:09,976
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

100
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:17,900
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

101
00:05:22,989 --> 00:05:24,615
Sir, clear!

102
00:05:24,699 --> 00:05:28,453
[PHONE VIBRATING]

103
00:05:28,536 --> 00:05:29,454
Sir?

104
00:05:29,537 --> 00:05:32,040
Areza, they're in the basement.
In the mechanical room.

105
00:05:32,123 --> 00:05:33,207
Alert all units.

106
00:05:33,291 --> 00:05:34,125
Yes, sir.

107
00:05:34,208 --> 00:05:35,293
[PHONE BEEPS]

108
00:05:35,376 --> 00:05:37,086
Sorry, Lucas.

109
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:42,717
[SOBS] Please, no…

110
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,927
All units, attention.

111
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:47,972
Emil Padua and his group
have been located.

112
00:05:48,056 --> 00:05:51,392
They're in the mechanical room,
basement level.

113
00:05:51,476 --> 00:05:54,771
All units in the vicinity,
proceed with caution.

114
00:05:54,854 --> 00:05:55,897
[RADIO STATIC]

115
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,940
- Let's move!
- Move!

116
00:05:58,024 --> 00:06:03,362
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,823
Don't let go of Mommy.

118
00:06:05,907 --> 00:06:07,033
You're okay.

119
00:06:09,786 --> 00:06:10,912
Don't worry, sweetie.

120
00:06:10,995 --> 00:06:17,251
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

121
00:06:18,503 --> 00:06:20,963
We're helpless, Mike.

122
00:06:24,217 --> 00:06:25,384
[EMIL] Are you ready?

123
00:06:27,095 --> 00:06:28,262
Go!

124
00:06:28,846 --> 00:06:29,806
[LUCAS] Blow it up!

125
00:06:29,889 --> 00:06:32,809
- [DETONATOR BEEPS]
- [LOUD EXPLOSION]

126
00:06:32,892 --> 00:06:35,353
[DISTANT EXPLOSION, GROUND RUMBLES]

127
00:06:35,436 --> 00:06:37,146
What was that? [WHIMPERS]

128
00:06:37,230 --> 00:06:38,397
It came from downstairs. Come on.

129
00:06:38,481 --> 00:06:41,067
- Come on, Ma.
- No, I don't want to go.

130
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:44,821
- You can't turn me in.
- I need to do this. I'm sorry, okay?

131
00:06:44,904 --> 00:06:47,031
- Let's go.
- No! I can't do this!

132
00:06:47,115 --> 00:06:48,449
[BODY THUDS]

133
00:06:48,533 --> 00:06:50,409
[GRETA PANTING]

134
00:06:50,493 --> 00:06:56,833
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

135
00:06:56,916 --> 00:06:58,543
Ma!

136
00:06:59,418 --> 00:07:05,967
[PEOPLE COUGHING, GRUNTING]

137
00:07:09,095 --> 00:07:10,972
[GROANS, COUGHS]

138
00:07:11,556 --> 00:07:14,016
Hey! Engineer!

139
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:15,935
Check if the tunnel is passable.

140
00:07:16,018 --> 00:07:19,522
I told you already that blowing it up
could make the tunnel collapse.

141
00:07:19,605 --> 00:07:20,731
It's not safe!

142
00:07:20,815 --> 00:07:22,024
[TENSE MUSIC]

143
00:07:22,108 --> 00:07:25,570
I said check if the tunnel is passable.

144
00:07:26,737 --> 00:07:28,072
Now!

145
00:07:28,156 --> 00:07:29,407
Go.

146
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:31,742
[EMIL COUGHS]

147
00:07:33,911 --> 00:07:36,956
[COUGHING]

148
00:07:37,915 --> 00:07:43,963
[COUGHING CONTINUES]

149
00:07:44,046 --> 00:07:50,845
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

150
00:07:52,638 --> 00:07:55,683
[PEOPLE COUGHING]

151
00:07:55,766 --> 00:07:58,811
[RUMBLING, DEBRIS FALLING]

152
00:07:58,895 --> 00:08:00,813
[COUGHING]

153
00:08:07,695 --> 00:08:10,615
[DEBRIS FALLING]

154
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:16,913
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

155
00:08:17,788 --> 00:08:21,918
[COUGHING]

156
00:08:23,044 --> 00:08:25,505
[EMIL COUGHING]

157
00:08:26,422 --> 00:08:29,175
[DEBRIS FALLING]

158
00:08:29,258 --> 00:08:35,932
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

159
00:08:36,015 --> 00:08:37,934
[FIRE CRACKLING]

160
00:08:40,353 --> 00:08:46,901
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

161
00:08:50,571 --> 00:08:51,822
[GROANS]

162
00:08:53,241 --> 00:08:54,450
[COUGHS]

163
00:08:57,453 --> 00:09:02,625
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

164
00:09:02,708 --> 00:09:04,794
[DEBRIS FALLING]

165
00:09:08,047 --> 00:09:10,174
[GRUNTS]

166
00:09:11,842 --> 00:09:14,053
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

167
00:09:14,136 --> 00:09:16,347
[WHEEZES, COUGHS]

168
00:09:23,854 --> 00:09:25,314
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC SWELLS]

169
00:09:25,398 --> 00:09:28,776
[GRUNTS, COUGHS]

170
00:09:31,571 --> 00:09:33,614
[GRUNTS, COUGHS]

171
00:09:34,657 --> 00:09:37,076
[COUGHING]

172
00:09:38,119 --> 00:09:43,833
[COUGHING]

173
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:47,378
Hon?

174
00:09:47,461 --> 00:09:51,048
[PEOPLE COUGHING]

175
00:09:51,132 --> 00:09:53,426
- Daddy?
- [MIKE COUGHS, GROANS]

176
00:09:54,093 --> 00:09:55,845
- [COUGHS]
- Honey.

177
00:09:56,596 --> 00:09:57,930
How is it, Engineer?

178
00:10:00,057 --> 00:10:02,435
There's an opening
leading to the old sewage line.

179
00:10:03,019 --> 00:10:07,315
But as I warned you beforehand, the walls
and the upper section are damaged.

180
00:10:07,398 --> 00:10:10,484
The temporary frames
and posts are also on fire.

181
00:10:11,485 --> 00:10:12,737
So if I were you,

182
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,614
I'd hurry, immediately.

183
00:10:15,197 --> 00:10:17,116
Gwen, you and Leni go ahead.

184
00:10:17,199 --> 00:10:19,327
You, take the bags.

185
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:21,203
- Move it! Go!
- Yes, sir.

186
00:10:21,287 --> 00:10:22,913
While the fire's still small!

187
00:10:22,997 --> 00:10:24,081
Come on, hurry!

188
00:10:24,582 --> 00:10:26,751
Help Leni, help her!

189
00:10:27,668 --> 00:10:29,045
- Go ahead, Gwen.
- [LENI GRUNTS]

190
00:10:29,128 --> 00:10:32,965
- Leni, go! Go with Gwen.
- [MEN COUGHING]

191
00:10:33,633 --> 00:10:36,385
- Here.
- Carry this.

192
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:40,806
- [SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]
- [MAN] Here you go.

193
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,933
Guard the exits!

194
00:10:44,518 --> 00:10:46,187
[RETCHES]

195
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:52,109
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

196
00:10:54,028 --> 00:11:00,576
[MEN COUGHING]

197
00:11:09,043 --> 00:11:10,336
Let's go.

198
00:11:10,419 --> 00:11:11,754
[LENI COUGHING]

199
00:11:13,547 --> 00:11:14,715
Leni.

200
00:11:15,674 --> 00:11:17,718
[LENI COUGHING]

201
00:11:17,802 --> 00:11:19,053
Move faster!

202
00:11:19,929 --> 00:11:21,639
Hurry up, this place is about to collapse!

203
00:11:21,722 --> 00:11:28,646
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

204
00:11:47,832 --> 00:11:48,791
[MAN GRUNTS]

205
00:11:48,874 --> 00:11:55,506
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

206
00:11:56,674 --> 00:11:58,217
[MAN GRUNTS]

207
00:12:09,895 --> 00:12:12,022
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

208
00:12:13,065 --> 00:12:14,608
[DADO] Give me that.

209
00:12:15,401 --> 00:12:16,652
[MAN GRUNTS]

210
00:12:16,735 --> 00:12:17,945
The bag.

211
00:12:19,989 --> 00:12:21,031
The bag.

212
00:12:24,243 --> 00:12:25,744
- [MAN 1 GRUNTS]
- [MAN 2] Here.

213
00:12:26,495 --> 00:12:33,461
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

214
00:12:38,632 --> 00:12:39,925
[MEN COUGHING]

215
00:12:40,009 --> 00:12:41,635
Get the engineer's family.

216
00:12:41,719 --> 00:12:43,471
We still need them.

217
00:12:43,554 --> 00:12:44,472
Engineer!

218
00:12:44,555 --> 00:12:46,807
[MADDIE] Daddy! Daddy, no!

219
00:12:46,891 --> 00:12:48,392
[MIKE] Stay here.

220
00:12:48,476 --> 00:12:49,477
I'll talk to them.

221
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:52,396
- Be careful.
- Daddy!

222
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,982
[MEN COUGHING]

223
00:12:56,192 --> 00:13:01,322
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

224
00:13:01,405 --> 00:13:02,490
[GUNSHOTS]

225
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:03,908
[DADO] Boss Emil!

226
00:13:03,991 --> 00:13:06,285
Put your guns down!
Put them down!

227
00:13:06,368 --> 00:13:08,162
- Hey!
- Put that down!

228
00:13:08,245 --> 00:13:09,455
Throw it into the hole!

229
00:13:11,415 --> 00:13:12,458
That gun too!

230
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:17,171
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

231
00:13:17,254 --> 00:13:18,547
I'll kill him!

232
00:13:18,631 --> 00:13:20,716
- Minnie! Minnie, run now!
- Mike!

233
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:23,260
- Run! Hurry!
- What about you?!

234
00:13:24,303 --> 00:13:26,013
- Let's go, baby.
- [MIKE] Put your guns down!

235
00:13:26,096 --> 00:13:27,765
- Daddy!
- Run! Run!

236
00:13:27,848 --> 00:13:28,682
[MINNIE] Okay!

237
00:13:28,766 --> 00:13:31,560
Don't touch my family, or I'll kill him!

238
00:13:31,644 --> 00:13:33,270
- I'll kill him!
- Go, baby! Go, baby!

239
00:13:33,354 --> 00:13:34,230
Run!

240
00:13:35,022 --> 00:13:36,190
Move!

241
00:13:39,109 --> 00:13:40,194
I'll kill him!

242
00:13:41,070 --> 00:13:42,863
You, go there!

243
00:13:42,947 --> 00:13:44,240
Get out of there!

244
00:13:46,283 --> 00:13:48,410
[BREATHING HEAVILY, COUGHING]

245
00:13:48,494 --> 00:13:50,496
This way, baby. Okay?

246
00:13:51,288 --> 00:13:52,957
Wait for me.

247
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:56,001
[COUGHING]

248
00:13:57,253 --> 00:13:58,170
Slowly, sweetheart.

249
00:13:59,046 --> 00:14:01,298
[EMIL GRUNTING] Ow!

250
00:14:01,382 --> 00:14:02,716
[MIKE] Don't follow us!

251
00:14:03,634 --> 00:14:05,261
I'll kill him, I swear!

252
00:14:05,344 --> 00:14:06,720
No one follows!

253
00:14:06,804 --> 00:14:08,138
Don't you dare take a step!

254
00:14:08,847 --> 00:14:10,349
This way!

255
00:14:12,268 --> 00:14:15,604
[COUGHING]

256
00:14:15,688 --> 00:14:16,855
Wait!

257
00:14:16,939 --> 00:14:19,316
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

258
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,734
Follow me, follow me.

259
00:14:21,569 --> 00:14:23,279
Careful, okay? Be careful.

260
00:14:23,362 --> 00:14:24,738
[MADDIE] Okay, Mommy.

261
00:14:25,823 --> 00:14:28,284
[WHIMPERING]

262
00:14:29,493 --> 00:14:30,828
This way.

263
00:14:36,292 --> 00:14:37,668
[MIKE] I'll kill him!

264
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:42,756
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

265
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,216
[DADO] Move!

266
00:14:48,929 --> 00:14:49,972
[MINNIE] Go, baby.

267
00:14:53,309 --> 00:14:54,602
Go.

268
00:14:55,102 --> 00:14:57,605
[COUGHING]

269
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:06,989
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

270
00:15:07,698 --> 00:15:09,742
[LIAM] You've got nowhere left to run, Ma.

271
00:15:11,243 --> 00:15:14,914
[COUGHING]

272
00:15:14,997 --> 00:15:16,206
Turn yourself in.

273
00:15:16,290 --> 00:15:18,334
Liam, I'm begging you.

274
00:15:18,417 --> 00:15:20,127
[COUGHS, SOBS]

275
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:21,587
Let's start over!

276
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:24,173
You, me, and your father.

277
00:15:24,256 --> 00:15:25,883
Let's run away.

278
00:15:25,966 --> 00:15:29,219
Let's go somewhere no one knows about.

279
00:15:29,303 --> 00:15:30,679
[LIAM COUGHS]

280
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:32,306
Do you even hear yourself, Ma?!

281
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:34,350
Do you want us to be criminals?!

282
00:15:34,433 --> 00:15:40,689
[BOTH COUGHING AGGRESSIVELY]

283
00:15:40,773 --> 00:15:41,857
Ma!

284
00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:44,068
Ma! [BREATHING HEAVILY]

285
00:15:44,151 --> 00:15:45,486
Ma!

286
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:50,407
[LIAM GROANING]

287
00:15:50,491 --> 00:15:51,659
[GRUNTS]

288
00:15:52,493 --> 00:15:55,037
Keep walking!

289
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,456
Keep walking! Move!

290
00:15:58,666 --> 00:16:00,000
Keep walking!

291
00:16:00,084 --> 00:16:02,628
Hey! Why are you here?!

292
00:16:03,379 --> 00:16:04,922
- Don't follow us!
- Hold on!

293
00:16:06,090 --> 00:16:08,133
Don't follow us! Come on! Tell them!

294
00:16:08,926 --> 00:16:11,053
Move back! Tell them!

295
00:16:11,136 --> 00:16:12,096
Tell them!

296
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:14,890
[GRUNTS]

297
00:16:14,974 --> 00:16:16,392
[GUN COCKS, GUNSHOT]

298
00:16:17,893 --> 00:16:24,817
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

299
00:16:29,321 --> 00:16:30,447
[GRUNTS]

300
00:16:30,531 --> 00:16:33,617
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

301
00:16:33,701 --> 00:16:35,327
- [LUCAS] Take cover!
- [EMIL] Move!

302
00:16:40,499 --> 00:16:41,709
[EMIL] Move!

303
00:16:44,378 --> 00:16:45,295
[LUCAS] Sit down.

304
00:16:45,379 --> 00:16:49,466
[GUNSHOTS]

305
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:50,843
[LUCAS] Dado!

306
00:16:50,926 --> 00:16:52,177
Boss.

307
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,013
Dado.

308
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:57,057
[DADO] I got this. You should leave now.

309
00:16:57,850 --> 00:16:59,476
- Dado…
- Hurry!

310
00:17:00,269 --> 00:17:01,687
Use this!

311
00:17:02,896 --> 00:17:04,398
You can do this.

312
00:17:05,691 --> 00:17:06,942
[EMIL] Keep shooting!

313
00:17:07,026 --> 00:17:11,530
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [METAL CLANKING]

314
00:17:15,409 --> 00:17:16,785
Dado, we'll get going!

315
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:24,585
[GUNSHOTS]

316
00:17:27,171 --> 00:17:28,172
[GUN COCKS]

317
00:17:28,255 --> 00:17:31,008
[GUNSHOTS]

318
00:17:31,091 --> 00:17:33,302
[GROANING]

319
00:17:40,809 --> 00:17:43,812
[GROANING]

320
00:17:45,230 --> 00:17:49,151
[GROANING CONTINUES]

321
00:17:50,986 --> 00:17:53,197
[GUNSHOTS]

322
00:17:54,364 --> 00:17:55,991
- [MIKE GROANING]
- Clear.

323
00:17:56,533 --> 00:17:58,285
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

324
00:18:04,416 --> 00:18:05,375
[LIGHTER CLICKS]

325
00:18:08,170 --> 00:18:11,381
[FUSE FIZZES]

326
00:18:13,842 --> 00:18:16,637
[GUNSHOTS]

327
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:20,390
[BOMB TICKING]

328
00:18:21,683 --> 00:18:24,645
- [EXPLOSION BOOMS]
- [DEBRIS THUDS]

329
00:18:24,728 --> 00:18:30,818
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

330
00:18:31,652 --> 00:18:35,197
[FOOTSTEPS RETREATING]

331
00:18:42,538 --> 00:18:44,039
<i>Where's Maddie?</i>

332
00:18:44,123 --> 00:18:45,582
<i>- Maddie.</i>
- [MIKE]<i> Where's Maddie?</i>

333
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:48,043
<i>- We have to find Maddie!</i>
<i>- Maddie!</i>

334
00:18:49,711 --> 00:18:51,004
<i>Liam! Liam!</i>

335
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:56,260
<i>We need to go back for Papa!</i>

336
00:18:56,343 --> 00:18:58,679
<i>We don't know where he could be.</i>

337
00:18:59,304 --> 00:19:03,475
<i>We requested that you be transferred here</i>
<i>to our hospital in Manila.</i>

338
00:19:03,559 --> 00:19:05,936
<i>- Where's Mama?</i>
<i>- Do you know anything?</i>

339
00:19:06,979 --> 00:19:09,231
<i>Is it true your mom was involved?</i>

340
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:13,443
If there's anyone who'd know
Greta Roja's whereabouts,

341
00:19:14,736 --> 00:19:16,071
<i>that'd be you, Mr. Roja.</i>

342
00:19:16,155 --> 00:19:18,157
<i>Believe it or not,</i>

343
00:19:19,449 --> 00:19:22,327
<i>if I find out where my wife is hiding,</i>

344
00:19:22,411 --> 00:19:24,413
<i>I will surrender her to you myself.</i>

345
00:19:26,206 --> 00:19:28,292
<i>Shouldn't you be focusing more</i>

346
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:30,919
<i>on catching Lucas Sebastian</i>
<i>and his associates?</i>

347
00:19:32,796 --> 00:19:34,882
<i>What if he threatens to kill my wife?</i>

348
00:19:36,466 --> 00:19:37,593
<i>Or my son?</i>

349
00:19:39,928 --> 00:19:44,641
<i>What if they're already holding her</i>
<i>hostage right now, as we speak?</i>

350
00:19:46,018 --> 00:19:48,228
<i>The search operation</i>
<i>for the suspects is ongoing.</i>

351
00:19:49,229 --> 00:19:51,940
<i>A task force has been set up for that.</i>

352
00:19:53,317 --> 00:19:54,693
<i>Well, then, what do you need me for?</i>

353
00:19:54,776 --> 00:19:58,822
[POLICE SIREN BLARING]

354
00:19:58,906 --> 00:20:00,365
[THUDS]

355
00:20:01,658 --> 00:20:03,577
<i>People are angry at us.</i>

356
00:20:04,411 --> 00:20:07,706
<i>Dude, they don't know anything.</i>

357
00:20:08,332 --> 00:20:10,167
<i>I'm just thinking about Mama.</i>

358
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,418
<i>Wherever she is,</i>

359
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,880
<i>I just know that she's not safe.</i>

360
00:20:15,839 --> 00:20:17,883
<i>So I hope she surrenders.</i>

361
00:20:22,262 --> 00:20:28,352
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
